{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard If a supplier is selected as One-Time Supplier, it is possible to enter address and tax information, AP supplier contact specifications, output media as well as payment method and payment address information at invoice entry, and connect this information to the individual invoice. The grouping of documents like checks or payment advices will be per address identity. (\b Note\b0 : The language for these documents and the country for selections/groupings will always be fetched from the master record not the individual invoice.) \par
One-Time Suppliers are only supported if the PAYLED module is installed. They are not supported in the PURCHASE module.\f0\par
}
